#StopAAPIHate

node.text:
From his parents, teammates, and home country of Georgia, @zazapachulia knows how important it is to have people in your corner in order to achieve your dreams
 
In My Court episode 2 looks at Zaza’s support system, and the support he provides his community
 
#YourPeopleMatter || @trinethr
